r initial body mass. Despite exposure to cool Ta in the cave, and often cold, wet, and windy conditions while foraging, or substantial food restriction in captive bats, R. aegyptiacus did not resort to using torpor.", "access_right": "restricted", "creators": [{"name": "Barclay, Robert M. R.", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Jacobs, David S.", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Harding, Craig T.", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "McKechnie, Andrew E.", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "McCulloch, Stewart D.", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Markotter, Wanda", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Paweska, Janusz", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Brigham, R. Mark", "affiliation": null}], "keywords": ["Biodiversity", "Mammalia", "Chiroptera", "Chordata", "Animalia", "bats", "bat"], "related_identifiers": [{"identifier": "hash://md5/bebd2121b889ed6f39db1d08426fe1d6", "relation": "hasVersion", "scheme": "url"}, {"identifier": "hash://sha256/4912be8864ef9da136c39b1e76fa31f1df33931ef0e442b26eae6930cdd58c59", "relation": "hasVersion", "scheme": "url"}, {"identifier": "zotero://select/groups/5435545/items/YZKTVBKV", "relation": "isDerivedFrom", "scheme": "url"}, {"identifier": "https://zotero.org/groups/5435545/items/YZKTVBKV", "relation": "isDerivedFrom", "scheme": "url"}, {"identifier": "https://linker.bio/cut:hash://md5/85694f0ccf99b1904128bce7b09dcac2!/b211220-213687", "relation": "isDerivedFrom", "scheme": "url"}, {"identifier": "hash://md5/330417efcaa2560c9b8ebcd6fae17ce0", "relation": "isPartOf", "scheme": "url"}, {"identifier": "10.5281/zenodo.1410543", "relation": "isCompiledBy", "resource_type": "software", "scheme": "doi"}], "custom": {"dwc:class": ["Mammalia"], "dwc:kingdom": ["Animalia"], "dwc:order": ["Chiroptera"], "dwc:phylum": ["Chordata"]}, "resource_type": {"title": "Journal article", "type": "publication", "subtype": "article"}, "journal": {"issue": "2", "pages": "572-578", "title": "Journal of Mammalogy", "volume": "98"}, "alternate_identifiers": [{"identifier": "h